version_description: Simple chords but complex structure. Use this video for strumming pattern https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VgF_6bXIAnA.
Slightly more accurate than the chords already here. Instrumental and outro included. From the Become You songbook.
Fixes some chords and verses, cleans up formatting and timing (critical for this fast and off-metered song).
The tab for the intro and outro is included - In the original, it's played on two guitars, but it's tabbed it so it can be played on one.
Unsure of some of the chords. Feel free to improve this. The basic progression is correct.
You need to watch them play it on YouTube for the complex strumming pattern. They seem to use some simpler chords live, too.

song_name: Dont Give That Girl A Gun

version_description: Transcribed mainly from this video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZWGTuhVGB3M Feel free to improve the accuracy.
You need to tune your B string down to A for this song (EADGAE). Emily plays it by picking the chords but it sounds fine strummed gently.
